node.text: This cake from @sashimi1 is a stunning masterpiece. Each layer of this showstopping Lemon Chiffon Cake with Blueberry-Coriander Buttercream gets a lift from eggwhite-enriched cake batter and flavor-packed flourishes. Edible flower petals, mint leaves, pools of glistening jam, fresh berries, and sliced citrus channel serious summer vibes. Tap the link in bio for this epic layer cake recipe!

node.title: Lemon Chiffon Cake with Blueberry-Coriander Buttercream

node.text: This week F&W Culinary Director at Large @justinchapple  takes a cue from regional barbecue sauces to create three bold dressings to transform summer salads into hearty main dishes. Full of flavor and inspiration, Texas Barbecue Sauce Vinaigrette, Sweet and Tangy Mustard Dressing and Alabama-style White Barbecue Dressing will punch up any salad green on the plate. Find out how to add some 'cue to your greens through the link in bio.

node.text: Heavy cream, a sprinkle of salt and copious amounts of butter transform the humble potato into the ultimate mashed potatoes. Michelin-starred chef Joël Robuchon is famous worldwide for his supersilky, superrich, superlight and buttery potatoes and this recipe is the late Anthony Bourdain's version of that classic. Tap the link in bio to try them for yourself. 📸: @bobbyfisherphotography

node.text: Salty, buttery, and slightly sharp, Comté cheese crisps similarly to Parmesan, adding an irresistibly crunchy layer to this Crispy Comté Frico Cheeseburgers recipe. This Ricotta-Orange Pound Cake with Prosecco Strawberries from @giadadelaurentiis is a simple, single-layered dessert. The orange zest and Amaretto-infused batter bakes up golden and sweet and makes a perfect companion to berries sprinkled with Prosecco and a little sugar. Tap the link in bio for the recipe! 
📸: @conpoulos_photographer

node.text:
Glazed and sweet, peppery and smoky, sliced, diced, crispy, (even floppy) and everything in between, we think bacon is the best thing on Earth. From BLT Smash Burgers to classic Quiche Lorraine and Chile Crisp-Glazed bacon we rounded up 33 of our favorite bacon recipes that will put your favorite ingredient in the spotlight. Tap the link in bio for all of those recipes and more.
Photo 📸: @gregdupree
Food Styling 🥓: @cspollen
Prop Styling 🍴: @chelseaczimmer

🍩: @antarasinha 📸: @protazio

node.text: This cake from @sashimi1 is a stunning masterpiece. Each layer of this showstopping Lemon Chiffon Cake with Blueberry-Coriander Buttercream gets a lift from eggwhite-enriched cake batter and flavor-packed flourishes. Edible flower petals, mint leaves, pools of glistening jam, fresh berries, and sliced citrus channel serious summer vibes. Tap the link in bio for this epic layer cake recipe!

node.text: Did you know Sidecars have been quenching our thirst for a good cocktail for 100 years? Guess they’re a classic for a reason. If you want to have one with dinner, Chef Ashleigh Shanti (@foodordeath_) recommends pairing it with a smoky ham that’s going to make the citrus notes shine. Find out how to make your own Sidecar using @remymartinus through the link in bio. #Sponsored
